FuncDef: Use this command to display information about the SAA test.

ParaDef.Info: The optional parameter is used to enter the name of the SAA test for which the information needs to be displayed. The test name must already be configured in the config>saa>test context.
Specifies the owner of an SAA operation, up to 32 characters. If a test-owner value is not specified, tests created by the CLI have a default owner "TiMOS CLI". ParamDefault: Default- "TiMOS CLI"
